Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.82,0:00:13.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:15.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:22.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:24.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.04,0:00:30.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不好意思  请问你是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就如你所见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:38.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看不太清
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:41.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是人神  是神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.06,0:00:45.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,人神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:46.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我一直在看着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.19,0:00:50.28,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这不是度过了很有趣的人生嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,偷窥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对  因为很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.53,0:00:56.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以我一直注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:00:59.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我觉得你正感到为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:02.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是你的同伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:04.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.83,0:01:05.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,笑死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.00,0:01:08.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,让我做异世界转生之类的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:10.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,结果还是Game Over了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看着我这么快活很开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:14.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,完全无法相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.01,0:01:16.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,总而言之我先给你个建议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:19.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就是有你这种人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.97,0:01:21.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,前世的时候也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.02,0:01:24.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说着给建议来诱惑我的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:28.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要有心就总有办法做到的年纪早就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.81,0:01:30.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就算变得积极
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.27,0:01:32.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,最后都只会变成加倍的绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:33.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就像现在这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.11,0:01:38.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不要误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.07,0:01:41.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我不是在说前世的事  是在说现在的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那我这个样子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:47.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是你的精神体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,肉体没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那等我醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:54.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不会回到这副像屎一样的身体是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:58.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等你醒了  你的身体也会恢复原来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊  是梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.47,0:02:04.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也很惊讶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,精神体和肉体居然有这么大差别
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以  你说要我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:14.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是异物很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以要我回原来的世界吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.74,0:02:17.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.32,0:02:20.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在这六面世界之外的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即便是我也没法把人送回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,也就是说  让我转生到这个世界的不是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.12,0:02:28.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,算是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:32.38,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这种事是邪恶的龙神擅长做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.67,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,邪恶的龙神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以要听吗  我的建议
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:37.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不听
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:39.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.47,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只听最开始的这次就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:45.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:47.89,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这种像「只放前端进去就好了」的讲法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:49.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,绝对是骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:51.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽说这样下去的话  你会死哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,会死？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:00.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:03.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔大陆是个非常严酷的大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:05.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,几乎没什么吃的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.08,0:03:07.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,还有很多魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:09.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你能挺过去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:11.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,等一下  那是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:12.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.38,0:03:16.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,被卷入到大规模的魔力灾害中  被转移了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:20.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔力灾害  是指那束光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.47,0:03:23.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.76,0:03:26.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在未知的危险土地上活下去的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:34.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,知道了  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.98,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不管是建议还是什么都好随便你说不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:38.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.32,0:03:39.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:41.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:43.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.66,0:03:48.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你醒来之后  附近会有个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.62,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,依靠那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:57.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,并且帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:36.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:45.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,基列奴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,基列奴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:23.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.18,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:32.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,是神的使者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道你的提问是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:41.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你们是从天上掉下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,人族的孩子很孱弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:47.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以生了篝火给你们暖身子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.28,0:05:48.16,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,你救了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:50.37,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你救了我们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:58.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,话说  这附近还有另外一名兽人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我只发现你们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.21,0:06:05.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你看见我不害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.85,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对救了自己的人感到害怕是很失礼的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:19.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你真是个不可思议的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:29.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是鲁迪乌斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德·斯佩路迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:39.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请让我坐在旁边  失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那个  这里是哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔大陆的东北  比耶寇亚地区
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,到了相当遥远的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:01.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,从这里回到中央大陆要费多长时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你们怎么会出现在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:09.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这大概是被卷入到大规模的魔力灾害中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:14.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我一定会送你们回故乡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:27.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,放任不管的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:30.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有损斯佩路德族的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:34.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,虽然这份尊严早已满身疮痍了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.64,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,艾莉丝  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.40,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这位是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:45.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,斯…斯佩路德…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.44,0:07:46.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.07,0:07:52.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,基列奴  基列奴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,为什么不过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对不起  鲁迪乌斯  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:07:58.45,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,把你撞飞了对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:08:01.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没有遵守约定对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:01.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对不…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那才是正常的反应
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我的反应是很异常的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:12.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,很异常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:14.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.01,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,并不坏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:26.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,初次…见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.11,0:08:32.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是艾莉丝·伯…伯雷亚斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.40,0:08:35.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,艾莉丝·伯伯伯雷亚斯·格雷拉特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:38.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不对  是伯雷亚斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:40.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只是稍微结巴了下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:44.75,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是瑞杰路德·斯佩路迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:54.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要能沟通  大家就能成为朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,母亲大人根本就是骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,还说不早点睡的话  斯佩路德族就会来吃人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:05.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就缩蜷起来装睡了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:06.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,别当我是傻子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.98,0:09:08.69,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,向瑞杰路德先生拜托的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.36,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我们或许就能成为朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.86,0:09:13.74,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:17.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也拜托瑞杰路德先生您了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:19.45,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.12,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,艾莉丝  请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:28.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,没办法  我就做你的朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:30.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.92,0:09:32.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在夜里两个人关系变得要好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:36.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即便不再害怕的艾莉丝说了失礼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德非常爽快没有在意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.05,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是哪个家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,传播斯佩路德族易怒的谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,突然来到未知的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这之后会是长途旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.28,0:09:55.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,必须把艾莉丝平安送回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:13.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,魔大陆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.42,0:10:16.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冒险开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我说过绝对不要动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,为什么没看见却知道有魔物在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:20.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,多亏了额头上的眼睛  我能看见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:21.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,真方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.03,0:11:25.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我不止一次想过没有这种东西就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那不如给我吧  把它挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:29.87,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:31.50,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是在开玩笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.63,0:11:34.84,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要是有把剑的话  我也能战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:37.71,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我也能用魔法帮点忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.42,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,小孩子不用操多余的心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.97,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就待在哥哥身边  让他保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,谁是我哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.68,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我才是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.81,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是这样吗  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可怜的瑞杰路德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是村庄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:02.11,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.32,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不能让他们进村子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.62,0:12:07.62,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,难道你要对小孩见死不救吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:08.74,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛因
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.08,0:12:10.79,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,他们是灾害的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.54,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,才被扔到这个地方而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:15.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,喂  他们在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,说我们很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:18.21,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以不让我们进村
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.05,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:21.97,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛因…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.55,0:12:23.93,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他们去通知村长了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.43,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,商量一下应该就可以进村吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那是心灵感应
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.20,0:12:45.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,米格路德族即使相隔很远也能对话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,米格路德族…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.79,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,村长  拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:52.83,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,就是这两个小孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.17,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:12:56.67,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我是鲁迪乌斯·格雷拉特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:12:58.59,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,好有礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,幸好学过魔神语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:03.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我是村长洛克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.01,0:13:08.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这个项链是在哪得到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:10.51,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他懂人类语的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是师傅给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.73,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,哦  师傅？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:16.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,名字是洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.02,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.36,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:22.82,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:24.11,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.11,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.83,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我女儿的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:35.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这里是洛琪希的老家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.05,0:13:44.92,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,鲁迪乌斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,有个奇怪的东西在保护田地呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:49.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,仔细一看才发现这是龟壳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一个洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:57.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,两个洛琪希
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.40,0:14:00.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,三个洛琪希  四个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:03.65,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,冷静  我的神是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:05.36,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,洛琪希她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.36,0:14:07.95,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,自从女儿她离开村子以后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:10.07,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,已经有20年毫无音讯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:11.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,20年也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.66,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,米格路德族的寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.66,0:14:15.91,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,一般是多少岁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.92,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,没出什么意外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.42,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,一般能活200年吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:22.34,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,算起来今年她也已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.13,0:14:25.96,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,44…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.17,0:14:29.01,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,总而言之  洛琪希她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.14,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:33.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,现在她在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.89,0:14:34.89,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,根据书信所述
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:36.60,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,在西隆王国…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:37.68,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,一切安好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.90,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,是的…应该吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:43.15,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.28,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,平安就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.57,0:14:47.15,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:48.99,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,岳父…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:56.70,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要是保罗他们知道我没事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:00.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我们也在昨天晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:06.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,看见流星飞往各地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:08.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,注意到了这一异常现象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:10.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:15.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.91,0:15:36.66,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你们俩关系挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.91,0:15:37.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:42.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那么他们打算怎么回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:44.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我会跟着他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:45.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不会只让他们两个人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你跟着他们  打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.80,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那还用说  由我来保护他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:55.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,护送他们平安回到家乡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:58.72,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,汝无法进城的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.27,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不能进城吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:04.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,如果出了什么事情  我会救他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:09.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,即使把那里的人们都杀光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,还是以和以前一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:15.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,只要一扯上孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.33,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你就变得什么都不管不顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:22.08,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,你是在10年前救下她的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:28.46,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是你这样乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.55,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,究竟能否够达成你的目标呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:36.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,请问…是指什么目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.51,0:16:40.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德阁下的目标是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:45.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,希望洗刷掉斯佩路德族的恶名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:50.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这好像…不大可能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:52.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,洛琪希也忠告过我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:54.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,对于斯佩路德族的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:57.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,估计在这个世界上已经深入人心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.70,0:16:59.53,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,连艾莉丝都如此恐惧的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.99,0:17:02.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是斯佩路德族在战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:05.79,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,杀人不分敌我的事情是事实吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:06.83,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,不是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.42,0:17:13.59,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那是拉普拉斯的阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.68,0:17:19.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,拉普拉斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.10,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那家伙背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.31,0:17:26.56,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,能细说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:31.48,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在那之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:36.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德讲述了历史的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.07,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,长枪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.91,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.37,0:17:44.96,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他赏赐了长枪给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.13,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,长枪是斯佩路德族的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:53.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,当时也有人无法舍弃灵魂使用别的长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:57.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,距今400年前的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.76,0:17:59.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,统一魔族
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.31,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,从人族那里赢得权力的英雄拉普拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:05.35,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,作为其属下一起战斗的斯佩路德族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德他们最终还是接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:07.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,拉普拉斯赏赐的荣誉之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.90,0:18:13.03,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那支长枪非常强力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:15.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,以至于让人觉得无人能敌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:20.41,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是此时异变发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:25.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我们不知从何时起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:28.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,开始不分敌我地去袭击周围的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是谁都没有觉得奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.38,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,谁都没有发现到这个变化
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.09,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:42.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我们杀光了眼前的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.56,0:18:45.06,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,然后在最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:47.23,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,弑父弑母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,弑妻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.77,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,弑兄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.40,0:18:54.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,刺死了自己的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.24,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这支长枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.78,0:19:03.95,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是儿子为了将我从诅咒中解救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:07.20,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,用命换来的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:11.00,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,斯佩路德族的恶名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.34,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是因为我们轻易地相信了拉普拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:16.17,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,接受了诅咒之枪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.22,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,是给予我们的惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:22.26,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,所以作为战士长的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:25.18,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,必须由我来洗清罪名
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.31,0:19:33.19,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,400年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.57,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,他一直都是孤身一人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:38.86,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一直都很懊悔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.11,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,一直都很无力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:49.54,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,后悔…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.25,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:57.63,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,要是有身为人族小孩的我帮忙的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,可能会带来一些变化
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我会帮助你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.60,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:08.39,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我会尽力而为去帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.35,0:20:13.90,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.40,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,要走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:24.03,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.16,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,这位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:26.24,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.08,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我叫洛嘉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.87,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,师傅的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.16,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,太太好年轻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.87,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.87,0:20:35.54,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,我今年可是102岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.38,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,非…非常年轻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.96,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,要是见到洛琪希了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:40.26,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,跟她说偶尔回来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:41.51,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:42.97,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,岳父
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.97,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,可以让我这样称呼您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:46.68,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.10,0:20:47.93,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:49.35,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.77,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,方便的话请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.93,0:20:53.27,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,这个也请收下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,作为告诉我们洛琪希平安消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.23,0:20:57.56,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:00.19,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:08.16,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,非常感谢你们的好意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:10.99,Mushoku-Text - majin,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:24.88,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我约定好了要帮助瑞杰路德
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.30,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,生前的我就算是听过那些话以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:30.93,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,应该也会嗤之以鼻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:33.52,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,但是昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.44,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,我决定去相信他了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.94,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,那时的那些话很轻易地就感动了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.15,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在城外他保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.53,0:21:44.61,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,在城内我帮助他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.32,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,这是互相帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:51.58,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,瑞杰路德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.04,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,今后也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.79,0:21:55.29,Mushoku-Text,,0,0,0,,好
